Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,538)\i1}The overwhelming power of III's new Number, Atlantal, is striking me relentlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,538)\i1}Although Astral has vanished, he still lives within my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.02,0:00:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't afford to lose this duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you only have 200 LP left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me finish you off now, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set 2 cards face-down, and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up, for the sake of Astral who entrusted hope to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See for yourself, Astral, this is my {\i0}real{\i1} duel now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This... is the other power you left for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will not waste it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll bring it to 'Em!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my LP are lower than 1000, I can use Aspiring Emperor Hope as Overlay material,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CHAOS XYZ CHANGE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, Chaos No.39!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The messenger who turns chaos into light, Aspiring Emperor Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I get closer, I stretch my hand out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}towards that shining light leading towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I dream of a world that expands from my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't a clue of where things like dreams and hopes are at.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I run looking for it, I still can't seem to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I have fallen into a gap of truth and lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, our grand tale has yet to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's move on towards tomorrow, \Neven if our road begins to fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will jump forward, before all my\N strength completely drains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The closer I get, the further it becomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that truth that I must seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's to find hope that we desire from a future unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.93,0:02:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With a heart stronger than anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll learn to keep running up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the strength to win any battle, \Ndespite just how weak I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My purpose is to find,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with these invaluable friends of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future of the world expanding\N from my feet with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes! Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat it to 'Em, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it finally comes huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,488)}"Numbers 49: The End of a Fierce Fight! \NHope Ray VS Atlanthal"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hope Ray, your power definitely can bring III back to his senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,538)}I activate the effect of Overlay Eater from my graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,538)}By banishing this card from my graveyard, it can absorb one overlay unit from my opponent's Xyz monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and attach it to my own Xyz monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! Now Atlantal cannot use his effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come! I activate Hope Ray's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For every Overlay Unit I detached this turn, he gains 500 ATK,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will detach all 3 Overlay Units from Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OVERLAY CHARGE!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also due to this effect, for every Overlay Unit detached, Atlantal loses 1000 ATK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral no longer exists, so why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! He still exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lives within my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lives within my 'Bring it to 'Em'!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And keeps making me strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Aspiring Emperor Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This level of counterattack, I already foresaw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap activate! Thunder Pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card negates the attack that targets an OOParts monster, and ends the Battle Phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Yuma's attack was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like even Hope Ray's attack won't be able to hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch! It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon for me to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card, and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are quite persistent, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now our monster's ATK has returned to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have no chance of winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dra -...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So {\i0}that's{\i1} what Tron's been talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen well, III.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After obtaining this Crests power,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you shall be able to control No.6 Atlantal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But while this card gives you enormous power,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it will also take a huge toll on your mind and body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will defeat Yuma to meet your expectation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have faith in you, III.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you are such a strong child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this the price of using Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me I am still unable to control the Number?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I will definitely meet Tron's expectation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...what's happening to that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Yuma! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While it has no Overlay Units, during my Standby Phase, Atlantal halves each player's LP!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...he is willing to cut down his own LP...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet... I still have some LP remaining, III!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III...you...that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about me, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the price of the power I seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I will perish...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I will still protect my family for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will defeat you with this attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Atlantal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Hope Ray! \NDIVINE PUNISHMENT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! If this attack connects, then Yuma-kun will lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap activate! Battle Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my opponent's monster declares an attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this card ends the battle phase, and destroys the attacking monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap - ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe you actually endured all that III, so as promised,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will give the Number and {\i0}this{\i1} card to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Angolmois...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tron... this Trap card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just treat it as your Lucky Charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This card is the Card of Destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After its activation, I guess both you and your opponent won't be safe anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just in case, I decided to entrust this card to you as insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tron...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you will win using whatever means necessary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...against Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Continuous Trap, Angolmois!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card I can destroy one Equip card on my field,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then it negates the activation of my opponent's trap card and destroys it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To destroy my trap, he's even willing to lower Atlantal's ATK!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One strike will be enough! After all, you only have 100 LP left!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resume the attack, Atlantal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow Hope Ray out along with Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap activate! Half Unbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card protects Hope Ray from being destroyed by battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while halve the damage is inflicted to the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...\NHe only has 50 LP remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma... you are still struggling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I will let you to witness my true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, stop it! III!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't we already become friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma... I don't need friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still wish to talk to you more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to you about your family and my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap card I just activated, Angolmois, is the Card of Destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During my next turn, it will inflict damage to you and me, equal to the ATK of Machu Mach it destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, when my next turn comes, both of us will get blown off the field after receiving 2400 damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't be a simple draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this is an battle between Number holders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I won't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my sacrifice will satisfy Tron's expectation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can get back my family, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That darkness is approaching here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Te...Tetsuo-{\i1}kun{\i0}, this is just AR Vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could such a thing happen in reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th...this is...don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's reality?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh...shooot! - At this rate we will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, III!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S... strange... don't tell me the Dimension Gate has...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a card which will lead everything to destruction..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Crest power can't control it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:13:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Angolmois's power is capable of destroying the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that III used that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be....you gave that card to III?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angolmois is the card to opens the door of Valian.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's activated, it shall become unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, III! What on earth is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This duel, at this rate, will open the gate that connects the Different Dimension!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I...no...virtually everything will get sucked inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! I don't want that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I....I don't wish to annihilate the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it to 'Em!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just said that at this rate the door of Different Dimension would open, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will win this duel and prevent its opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible. With Atlantal's effect, when my LP are 1000 or lower,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cannot be destroyed by battle, and I take no battle damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking!! This duel is not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It' s too soon to give up right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, if Astral were here, he would still think about how to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use ZeXal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZeXal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the miraculous force summoned by Astral and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, there might be a way to call back Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Astral back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral has disappeared due to this Crest's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, if I pass on this power to you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... which means... he will come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you might not be able to tame this Crest's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And quite possibly, you might be engulfed by this power as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care! As long as I can get Astral back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, transfer your power to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I successfully transfer the Crest Power to Yuma,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am afraid I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:15:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I lose to the power of this Crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it to 'Em!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ASTRAL!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral, my son is calling for you. Please go help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard your voice. Let's win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you always act tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, Astral! Don't mind me, hurry up and defeat this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, use ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Let's go, Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will overlay you and myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With us both I will build an overlay network!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When two distant souls cross each other, the legendary power shall appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZeXal!\NZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma fused with Astral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything from the strongest duelist's duel is predetermined!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the draw shall be decided by the duelist as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, ZeXal Weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phoenix Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This monster can be equipped to Hope Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the equipped Hope Ray attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the battle damage will be negated,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and 1000 damage will be inflicted to my opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Atlantal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PHOENIX FINISH!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the bond between Yuma and Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! III was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, to summarize, we were saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I... win?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said we would win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ri...right, III!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III, III!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You recognize the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my {\i1}first{\i0}, and {\i1}last{\i0} friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:21:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, I have a favor to ask from you. Can you save my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can definitely do it, if someone can, it's you... with your 'Bring it to 'Em'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you got 5 Heart Pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are qualified for the Final.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III, I won't let your feelings go to waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will win... the Duel Carnival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it to 'Em
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright, III.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you please hold my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you could always hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... I feel quite tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will remain by your side, so have a good sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma Tsukumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma's son!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone gave me some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I was able to paint a rainbow with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to become someone perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even with me suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't seem to grasp victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:22:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must be having some kind of weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But If I must fulfill this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I don't mind being laughed at for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since it's because your limits are decided on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show it, overcoming it to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I'm aiming for the big blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For all of its glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of those countless flower petals
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They came at the expense of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}me being able to reach those heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.13,0:23:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, even though I lost my way today,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still yearn for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,584)}Finally, the Finals of WDC!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.67,0:23:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,584)}Duelists who past the preliminaries after surviving all kinds of intense battles, tonight, they will all gather in the Night Ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.89,0:24:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought Kotori and others with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.76,0:24:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The attendants are all strong duelists, don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? That guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.65,0:24:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eve of the Storm! The Diabolical Duelist appears - Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.33,0:24:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.97,0:24:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muzurhythm, Tenten Tempo, Mellowmellow Melody
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their effects will suit any tactical situation as the all are Rank 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.36,0:24:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon MuzuTenMelody Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.23,0:24:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least memorize the effects.
